Package: uroam
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, libc6 (>= 2.34), libgcc-s1 (>= 3.4), libstdc++6 (>= 5.0)
Description: Universal RAM Optimization Layer
 A system-level RAM optimization framework for Linux that intelligently
 manages memory usage across AI workloads, gaming, and general applications.
 .
 Features include:
  - Kernel-level memory tracking via kprobes/ftrace
  - NUMA-aware allocation in user-space
  - zRAM/zswap dynamic compression tuning
  - Page deduplication with KSM
  - eBPF-based allocation tracing
  - PyTorch/TensorFlow integration hooks
  - C/C++ client library

Package: uroam-dbg
Architecture: any
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, uroam (= ${source:Version})
Description: UROAM debug symbols
 Debug symbols for uroam memory optimization framework

Package: uroam-dev
Architecture: all
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, uroam (= ${source:Version}), cmake
Description: UROAM development files
 Development headers and libraries for uroam